This CMCG Slack group has become one of my favorite groups lately! :smile: I love reading the questions and tips from everyone.

I’ve followed some on Twitter and learned more about the diverse individuals in here.

:point_right: If you haven’t, please add some details to your Slack profile, like your website or Twitter handle!

Reading through responses in discussions, I will click on someone’s profile... and nothing :joy:

Am I the only one sad about not being able to connect with folks outside the group or learn more?
